{"title":"Welcome","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"Welcome"},"headingText":"Welcome to *Python for Beginners*","containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n\nWelcome! This course is designed for complete beginners who want to learn real Python by writing lots of code.\n\n## What you will learn\n\nBy the end of the first part of the course you will be able to:\n\n- write and run Python programs\n- use variables and arithmetic\n- ask the user for input\n- make decisions with `if`\n- repeat code with loops\n- work with lists\n\n## How to use this course\n\n1. Work through the lessons **in order**.\n2. Type every example into Positron yourself.\n3. Complete the exercises **before** opening the hints.\n4. Only look at the solutions if you are really stuck.\n5. Try the challenge exercises—they are where the real learning happens.\n\n## Course outline\n\n1. Getting Started with Positron\n2. Lesson 1 – Your First Python Program\n3. Lesson 2 – Making Python Interactive\n4. Lesson 3 – Making Decisions with `if`\n5. Lesson 4 – Repeating Code with Loops\n6. Lesson 5 – Lists and `for` Loops\n\nGood luck, and have fun!\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n# Welcome to *Python for Beginners*\n\nWelcome! This course is designed for complete beginners who want to learn real Python by writing lots of code.\n\n## What you will learn\n\nBy the end of the first part of the course you will be able to:\n\n- write and run Python programs\n- use variables and arithmetic\n- ask the user for input\n- make decisions with `if`\n- repeat code with loops\n- work with lists\n\n## How to use this course\n\n1. Work through the lessons **in order**.\n2. Type every example into Positron yourself.\n3. Complete the exercises **before** opening the hints.\n4. Only look at the solutions if you are really stuck.\n5. Try the challenge exercises—they are where the real learning happens.\n\n## Course outline\n\n1. Getting Started with Positron\n2. Lesson 1 – Your First Python Program\n3. Lesson 2 – Making Python Interactive\n4. 